Scenario 2: Book Class
Objective: Implement a class with fields and methods.

Instructions:

Implement the Book class with fields title (String) and author (String).
Add a method displayInfo to print the book details.
In the main method, create an object of the Book class and call the displayInfo method.

Note: The creation of objects using the main method is just for your understanding. It will not be evaluated. Only the classes will be evaluated.